  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ol><li><p>Preparation and submission of project documentations/ reports from commencement to completion of project (eg. Risk Assessment, requisitions, schedule, drawings, reports, etc).</p></li><li><p>Assist in planning for material, equipment and resource required according to project specifications and requirements and ensure budget and cost are in control</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with maincon, subcon, building owner, consultant, etc on project matters</p></li><li><p>Supervises technicians/ workers</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper filing of project documentations and reports</p></li><li><p>Prepare project activities and schedules report, etc</p></li><li><p>Assist in preparing quotes, propose or recommend works to customer to generate sales</p></li><li><p>Efficient planning and maintain positive productivity with allocated resources</p></li><li><p>Assist in preparations of quotations, attend site survey, when necessary</p></li><li><p>Provide administrative support to superior when necessary;</p></li><li><p>Any other duties suitable duties as and when assigned by the Company</p></li></ol><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma in any discipline or equivalent</p></li><li><p>At least 2 years of relevant working experience in M&E Engineering / Construction industry</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Office Applications</p></li><li><p>Good interpersonal and communication skill </p></li><li><p>Good planning, organizing, coordination and follow-up skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work under pressure with minimum supervision</p></li></ul><p><br /></p>",
