    "description": "<p>Donjon Pte Ltd (Donjon) is a Singapore-based company established in 2003.</p>\n\n<p>Donjon offers a wide spectrum of engineering services / solutions to industrial, commercial, residential and government sectors. </p>\n\n<p>Our Core Business involves technical testing and others M&E related contract works to both Private and public Sector.</p>\n\n<p>We have extensive experience in Installation of HT / LT Electrical Equipment, Upgrading, Retrofitting and replacement of Electrical Equipment, Preventive and Predictive Maintenance services and Air-conditioning and mechanical Ventilation works.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n",
